{"tid":161235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百厭兄弟闖校園搗亂 父母要賠近5個月人工","createTime":"2017-03-18T11:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T18:34:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e33740231fc00888fac7eec69d6718193da207","tid":161235,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【無家教】百厭兄弟闖校園搗亂 父母要賠近5個月人工<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170318/56439556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170318%2F56439556&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=2a82041e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170318%2F56439556&h=0a8d3dec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170318/56439556</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n泰國一對小兄弟，在暑假期間闖入一間學校搗亂，不但把書本教具撕碎搗毀，又把電腦電視全部推倒、把白板塗成黑色，教室像被轟炸過一般。他們的父母要賠償學校4萬泰銖(8,900港元)，約相等於5個月薪金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489768592_aea1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489768592_aea1.jpg&h=f06b20e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這對「破壞王」兄弟，分別只有8歲和9歲。他們趁泰國3、4月放暑假，闖入東北四色菊府一間小學肆意破壞。校工事後發現報警，警方根據線索找到這對兄弟，他們承認因為貪玩而闖禍。<br />\n<br />\n學校估計損失達6萬多泰銖(1.3萬多港元)，要求他們的父母賠償。但這對孖寶的父母只是建築工人，表示無力支付，經討價還價，學校最終同意只收4萬泰銖，並可分期付款。<br />\n<br />\n泰國建築工人一般月薪約9,000泰銖(2,000港元)，東北偏僻地區更可能拿不到此數。"},{"pid":"dfedc5eadca7cc10d2ea8d9e95c1e9668995cc04","tid":161235,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"做得好！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d96d46bff39990c643088086ae202a10c7bfb21","tid":161235,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:58:56.000Z","msg":"他們只是孩子呀"},{"pid":"eae3c17948b10cfeb622caa637e6b8a39fa8eb9f","tid":161235,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe46a1c7933e88cf2660eb9d0ad480e900c2245","tid":161235,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他們只是孩子呀</blockquote><br />\n所以只係賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a131a00dc92bdc2c58daa049e8857142090c1786","tid":161235,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>power_off<br />\n<br />\n極度懷疑年初一旺角暴動當日，有份參與暴動向警察投擲硬物，此人言論激進，維護港獨分子，麻煩有關人士要將此人納入觀察名單，慎防此人鼓吹或煽動他人犯罪。如有需要，請立刻上門調查。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c81330bb4148b6b5e9b7af4f28ee4564ade05868","tid":161235,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T18:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>power_off<br />\n<br />\n極度懷疑年初一旺角暴動當日，有份參與暴動向警察投擲硬物，此人言論激進，維護港獨分子，麻煩有關人士要將此人納入觀察名單，慎防此人鼓吹或煽動他人犯罪。如有需要，請立刻上門調查。</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>蛇仔明x臭Fing <br />\n極度懷疑佢係藍絲狗，完。<br />\n</strong></span>"}]}